item.title: Error When Compiling
item.dc:creator: @Bettencourtt Bettencourtt
item.description:
@Bettencourtt wrote:

Well that means you coded it wrong… If you can’t fix it worse is re download the source try to code everything all over again and for Changing exp

open client.java then do ctrl+f and search for (double) until you see
[tt] if (FightType == 1) // Accurate { TotalExp = (double) (750 * hitDiff); TotalExp = (double) (TotalExp * CombatExpRate); addSkillXP((int) (TotalExp), playerAttack); } else if (FightType == 2) // Agressive {[/tt] So 750 is the amount exp you get per hit for attack change that to like 20000 for fast training he will get attk lvl 66 on 1 hit and just scroll down to strength then defence Hp Hope it helps
